sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Voyageur
    participant S as RecommendationsScreen
    participant C as AppContext
    participant D as MockData
    participant E as RecommendationEngine

    U->>S: Ouvre l'ecran Recommendations
    S->>C: Lire preferences
    C-->>S: UserPreferences

    alt Preferences disponibles
        S->>S: useEffect() + delai de 700 ms
        S->>D: Charger destinations, activities, accommodations
        D-->>S: Donnees mockees
        S->>E: generateRecommendations(preferences, destinations, activities, accommodations)
        E->>E: Calculer le score des destinations
        E->>E: Selectionner les meilleures destinations
        E->>E: Filtrer les activites correspondantes
        E->>E: Filtrer les hebergements compatibles
        E->>E: Generer l'explication textuelle
        E-->>S: RecommendationResult
        S->>S: setRecommendations(result)
        S-->>U: Afficher destinations, activites et hebergements recommandes
    else Preferences absentes
        S->>S: setLoading(false)
        S-->>U: Afficher un etat sans recommandations
    end
